ng-progress-paradigm-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/destiny-2-changing-progress-paradigm-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/destiny-2-changing-progress-paradigm-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/destiny-2-changing-progress-paradigm-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bungie">Bungie</a>概述了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/destiny-2"><em>《命运 2》</em></a>随着第 22 季、第 23 季和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-fans-think-paul-mccartney-is-coming-back-for-a-new-soundtrack-3473012"><em>最终形态》</em></a>的到来而带来的各种变化，包括彻底修改的“具有全新机制的季节进程范式”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/el-paso-elsewhere-debuts-action-packed-music-video-for-stay-awake-3469857">“埃尔帕索，别处”首次推出动感十足的“保持清醒”音乐视频</a></strong></li></ul><p>“团队专注于确保第 20 至 23 季和<em>《最终形态》</em>之间的故事叙述中的结缔组织比去年的<em>《Lightfall》</em>季节更有影响力，”游戏总监 Joe Blackburn 在 Bungie 自己的博客上发表的一篇<a href="https://www.bungie.net/7/en/News/article/state_of_the_game_aug_2023" target="_blank" rel="noopener">文章</a>中说道。 。它补充说，已经听取了粉丝关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/destiny-2s-lightfall-expansion-fails-new-players-3408447">三月份推出<em>《Lightfall》</em>的</a>反馈，该章节被认为是一个薄弱的叙事章节。</p><p> Bungie 未来的目标是“扩展玩家的想象力”、“将挑战带回<em>《命运》</em> ”、“丰富我们的内容”以及“连接我们的守护者”。这将通过计划于 2023 年下半年推出的游戏修改来实现。</p><p>具体来说，这些需要第 22 季和第 23 季的游戏稳定性更新、仪式供应商的新武器以及新地图和模式，例如 Crucible 获得 Vex Multiplex 地图、Relic 模式和 Checkmate 修改器。 </p><figure id="attachment_3426864" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3426864" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3426864" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Destiny-2-Lightfall-feedback-changes.jpg" alt="《命运 2》。图片来源：Bungie。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Destiny-2-Lightfall-feedback-changes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Destiny-2-Lightfall-feedback-changes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Destiny-2-Lightfall-feedback-changes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Destiny-2-Lightfall-feedback-changes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Destiny-2-Lightfall-feedback-changes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Destiny-2-Lightfall-feedback-changes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3426864" class="wp-caption-text"> 《命运 2》。图片来源：Bungie。</figcaption></figure><p>另一方面，Gambit 正在接收伤疤大教堂地图以及暗影军团和朗讯蜂巢敌人类型。第 22 季引入了三个新的分支方面，即猎人的旋转漩涡、泰坦的战争旗帜和术士的编织行走。</p><p>此外，停滞方面和碎片将被转移到供应商系统，而转化物将变成解锁物品而不是消耗品。</p><p> “在不破坏展示之前的任何内容的情况下，我们的下一季将进入我们以前从未探索过的创意领域。我们正在大幅改变一些事情，包括采用全新机制的赛季进程范式，”布莱克本解释道，并补充说这对玩家来说将是“非常新且不同的”。</p><p> It&#39;s difficult to discern what this means on the scant detail that the studio was offering in the blog post, but more information will be provided on August 22.</p><p> In other gaming news, <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii">Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</a></em> seems to be a smash hit for <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a> , securing the title of the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-overtakes-sons-of-the-forest-to-become-steams-second-biggest-launch-of-2023-3478167">second most successful Steam launch of this year</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-is-changing-how-players-earn-progress-in-the-next-season-3478196">&#39;Destiny 2&#39; is changing how players earn progress in the next Season</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
